\s BENE DATA NITWUMVIRE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Bene Data nitwumvire impanuro Imana \bd*\bd Iduha\bd*\bd , tugir’ukwizera mu mitima yacu, nk’ukw’abana b’Imana ba mbere.\bd*
\pc \bdit Bar’ingenzi n’akavantara kw’isi bizer’Imana, iy’isi ntiyar’ibabereye, abo bose bapfuye bacizeye.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Bose bapfuye bacizey’Imana, batarabon’ivyasezeranywe; ariko barabibona biri kure, bakabisasirira.\bd*
\pc \bdit Bar’ingenzi n’akavantara kw’isi bizer’Imana, iy’isi ntiyar’ibabereye, abo bose bapfuye bacizeye.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Bifuz’igihugu kirushirije, iy’isi kuba iciza; ni co gituma batamaramazwa, no gushingir’Imana intahe. \bd*
\pc \bdit Bar’ingenzi n’akavantara kw’isi bizer’Imana, iy’isi ntiyar’ibabereye, abo bose bapfuye bacizeye.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Bose bamerewe nabi aha kw’isi, kukw’iy’isi atar’iy’iwabo; bashirwa mu ngoyi no mu mabohero abandi bicishwa amabuye.\bd*
\pc \bdit Bar’ingenzi n’akavantara kw’isi bizer’Imana, iy’isi ntiyar’ibabereye, abo bose bapfuye bacizeye.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd None mwene Data wakiwe n’umuco, ako n’akarorero keza; twifuze kumera nk’abo bizera, duhahamire ico gihugu.\bd*
